 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"011db237b92337b25e328fe5f201382641ba36a5","tid":289867,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T04:21:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>熱血時報已經冇人去做採訪，日日上網搵新聞黎轉載<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大種農場新聞<br />\n<br />\n不過佢冇用一張圖就作單哇眾取寵既假新聞咁解<br />\n<br />\n但都係抄黎抄去"},{"pid":"a9a6cbc3f4108380dc6bcc53c7a09ee178872474","tid":289867,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T04:25:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>熱血時報已經冇人去做採訪，日日上網搵新聞黎轉載<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大種農場新聞<br />\n<br />\n不過佢冇用一張圖就作單哇眾取寵既假新聞咁解<br />\n<br />\n但都係抄黎抄去</blockquote><br />\n日日睇rthk有咩新聞，執下d文字拎埋張圖就出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e432ec47ed5029e6bdd71d1171a5be94ecff7f3","tid":289867,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T04:27:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>熱血時報已經冇人去做採訪，日日上網搵新聞黎轉載<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大種農場新聞<br />\n<br />\n不過佢冇用一張圖就作單哇眾取寵既假新聞咁解<br />\n<br />\n但都係抄黎抄去</blockquote><br />\n日日睇rthk有咩新聞，執下d文字拎埋張圖就出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n運作成本同農場新聞一樣咁低<br />\n<br />\n然後仲有得收課金"}]}